data.description: Theres a reason many a real estate write ups start with location, location, location. Truth is, it matters, and this home nails it. Located between booming hubs of 114th and 123rd south, this baby is easily accessible from both Salt Lake and Utah Counties. That, plus nearby schools, plenty of outdoor recreation (explore: Corner Canyon), convenient shopping, means youre close to everything you need. The home itself boasts some pretty sweet bragging rights if we do say so ourselves. Deceptively sized from the street, this nearly new home was crafted with attention to detail throughout. The housing buzzword open concept couldnt be more applicable here. The kitchen - which has granite countertops, 18 tile, and a gas cooktop - is wide open to the enormous family room and walkout patio. Upstairs youll find the laundry room, 2 bathrooms and 3 total bedrooms including the large master suite with sky high vaults and huuuuge master bathroom. Relax, stretch out, and take a deep breath, youre home.
